  "text": "Cell apoptosis assay was performed as described previously [CITATION_1] using the Annexin V-FITC apoptosis detection kit (BD PharMingen, San Diego, CA). Briefly, human monocytes (5610 [CITATION_2] ) were incubated with inhibitors for 30 minutes in X-vivo medium and restimulated with 100 ng/ml M-CSF overnight. The cells were removed from the culture dish using Accutase (eBioscience, San Diego, CA) and stained with Annexin V-FITC and PI and analyzed by flow cytometry (FACSCalibur; BD PharMingen).",
